{"tid":181023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"放假係屋企煮咩好---番茄意大利麵","createTime":"2017-03-31T10:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T11:36:35.000Z","uid":97096,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7931f64e0898fe92dd10be834715f308db4e76","tid":181023,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"前幾日放假懶到唔想出街<br />\n於是就睇下屋企有咩可以煮黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知俾我發現到一包意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就打算簡簡單單既意粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Do199j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Do199j.jpg&h=67210ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先以下係屋企有既材料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/174535_f154c4e9d0de1b54aae2167b9d724287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F174535_f154c4e9d0de1b54aae2167b9d724287.jpg&h=e1e340d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.意粉<br />\n2.番茄<br />\n3.茄汁<br />\n4.黑椒粉<br />\n5.荷蘭豆<br />\n6.香草粉<br />\n7.鹽(唔記得影)<br />\n8.雞蛋(唔記得影)<br />\n基本上都係睇到屋企有咩就落咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著就準備一杯水，同埋將番茄同荷蘭豆洗乾淨，再切細件<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/175138_2aa43b37cadb35c7f4978a78c89b35a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F175138_2aa43b37cadb35c7f4978a78c89b35a0.jpg&h=d1b77c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將所有既材料放入個pan度一鑊熟(要加水)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Nq84R7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Nq84R7.jpg&h=5a903eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cEb97g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cEb97g.jpg&h=47e7fbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一時間，煲定水，打隻蛋落一個細兜，水滾就落兜蛋(連埋個兜）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6axXef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6axXef.jpg&h=8bf3e3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/175813_79bab6fc7c2c2a959a063b6fad3d4bfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F175813_79bab6fc7c2c2a959a063b6fad3d4bfb.jpg&h=ab1213c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢個時候，個pan d意粉應該淋咗，咁就打開蓋等佢收水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zW2EPxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzW2EPxB.jpg&h=dfc5d30c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/180059_15530b74816ad5990dbc5c6d245534f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F180059_15530b74816ad5990dbc5c6d245534f1.jpg&h=38b7b2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等到佢差唔多收乾就熄火，加一片仔牛油等佢香d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6a512B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6a512B.jpg&h=041a2f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撈到d牛油溶晒就可以上碟la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/an03Y9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fan03Y9q.jpg&h=b2b15d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nD蛋滾到轉白色，就可以放埋係意粉上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/180827_15067ded50357312f1a1a5bfd029360c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F180827_15067ded50357312f1a1a5bfd029360c.jpg&h=1f23ca64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZewkGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZewkGi.jpg&h=93c87d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建議隻蛋可以唔使煮咁耐，咁就更加流心la<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCc35ME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCc35ME.jpg&h=bda2b4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLLA5t0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLLA5t0.jpg&h=98b2f526&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b777c3ff4a7c0804e70fa3cc0c27fc652030a9f8","tid":181023,"uid":37758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"意粉就意粉<br />\n公仔麵就公仔麵<br />\n<br />\n你邊到鄉下呀"},{"pid":"88abef586865e35bf56eef3b85f088a180e035e9","tid":181023,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點"},{"pid":"35f205ab3da1777b8e573cc78ab068d5526785c9","tid":181023,"uid":25136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意粉就意粉<br />\n公仔麵就公仔麵<br />\n<br />\n你邊到鄉下呀</blockquote><br />\n意粉黎喎Ching"},{"pid":"86bbde89ae8eafa0be89d3965fe8d27139ed5c20","tid":181023,"uid":19309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"fdfa424d79b1442ba04e329f753dc1f01d189c5c","tid":181023,"uid":97096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點</blockquote><br />\n煮到收乾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D味點走？"},{"pid":"c9a7ea188d73f24f5157192db76eb462af1527b6","tid":181023,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df953170eb9294901d5b6612b8bcb72d56669239","tid":181023,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>意粉就意粉<br />\n公仔麵就公仔麵<br />\n<br />\n你邊到鄉下呀</blockquote><br />\n意粉黎喎Ching</blockquote><br />\n你邊度鄉下,意粉當公仔面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235761450ce55a8346e8ec108a6fecdbcfc31b34","tid":181023,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點</blockquote><br />\n煮到收乾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D味點走？</blockquote><br />\n好有創意!<br />\n<br />\n想知收水收左幾耐呀 ?"},{"pid":"516e3d3ec6a21820e51c07209672d856677aa91a","tid":181023,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:24:42.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以煮到d意粉水都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3507bf36647d0bc44039856dab955cefbe9152","tid":181023,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點</blockquote><br />\n煮到收乾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D味點走？</blockquote><br />\n好有創意!<br />\n<br />\n想知收水收左幾耐呀 ?</blockquote><br />\n其實正常煮意粉煮到熟為止已經會冇左半煲水 更何況嗰度咁撚少水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上正常煮汁都會落一殼意粉水<br />\n如果啲意粉煮過龍一眼就睇得出<br />\n變通下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2022c4b1a65bf2bfc6fdf92ccdad20b05add428b","tid":181023,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點</blockquote><br />\n煮到收乾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D味點走？</blockquote><br />\n好有創意!<br />\n<br />\n想知收水收左幾耐呀 ?</blockquote><br />\n其實正常煮意粉煮到熟為止已經會冇左半煲水 更何況嗰度咁撚少水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上正常煮汁都會落一殼意粉水<br />\n如果啲意粉煮過龍一眼就睇得出<br />\n變通下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實啲意粉係唔洗&quot;煮&quot;熟佢架<br />\n水滾熄火就可以焗淋佢"},{"pid":"6f7dd66881e35716984936aa9c106e48a8b6ce70","tid":181023,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"煮到收水 意粉應該淋晒<br />\n分開煮好似好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e7e6e6016d1b55daea59d20a23e14df0007c62","tid":181023,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"呢個係懶人做法 sell 1 take 過 唔係sell 味道<br />\n係咁叫人分開煮做乜春"},{"pid":"589747b8c7e2473baa5642254068dffbc86620ff","tid":181023,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個係懶人做法 sell 1 take 過 唔係sell 味道<br />\n係咁叫人分開煮做乜春</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好有道理"},{"pid":"1b40a97f8001fdba8d25fdb8d13fb33a205cad86","tid":181023,"uid":97096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以分開煮<br />\n煮走曬啲味，想點</blockquote><br />\n煮到收乾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D味點走？</blockquote><br />\n好有創意!<br />\n<br />\n想知收水收左幾耐呀 ?</blockquote><br />\n我用天使麵<br />\n五至十分鐘到就收水"},{"pid":"7548b17100e04fbc79145fb5a75ea6a8460e9ff2","tid":181023,"uid":97096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個係懶人做法 sell 1 take 過 唔係sell 味道<br />\n係咁叫人分開煮做乜春</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好有道理</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135465d7c49c1bf45d776e534bf6f3e6c4535084","tid":181023,"uid":25188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個係懶人做法 sell 1 take 過 唔係sell 味道<br />\n係咁叫人分開煮做乜春</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好有道理</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明外國都好多人教one pot cook d人係咪以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f3624919c4b9bd6160bdd1dd110339087559b1","tid":181023,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"啲豆放落煮蛋個煲仲好<br />\n而家成PAT嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7417a4bb45ce00fbcd163bfe82f507ed900a2fe","tid":181023,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}